{
  "texts": [
    "Generative AI opens the possibility of always-helpful, on-the-fly, continuous formative feedback and progress assessments that analyze everything a student has written within a class or course.6.",
    "Seize the Day, Take Control of the AI.",
    "It will, of course, be impossible to control unfiltered use of publicly accessible Generative AI.",
    "In their unfiltered form, so far they have been more frequently used for cheating than anything else.",
    "But layered over the foundation LLMs, educational software applications can be made more attractive to learners and their teachers than the unfiltered, publicly accessible chatbot sites."
  ]
}